Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼都不聯絡我一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你爽約不回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}優子的暑假計劃就完全浪費…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 我完全都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\c&HAC8DA3&\frx322\fry356\frz325.8\pos(1074.14,418.333)}向遊戲大獎邁進吧
